Package files

Class TrainSet

java.lang.Object
files.FileSet
files.TrainSet
public class TrainSet
extends FileSet
This class extends the FileSet class so it opens and correctly divides the Train File.

It created a Node for every Feature, with it's name, range and index; and this node is then added to the graph.
